data.description: Open 3 bedroom 3 1/2 bath townhouse with an additional 2 ft of space on all 3 levels in Leonardtown features hardwood on 1st floor, stainless steel appliances, granite counters and plenty of cabinet space.Finished basement with family room and full bath, laundry room on the upper level. Attached finished 2 car garage and deck.
